IMAPAccount mattusifer
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User mattusifer@gmail.com
PassCmd "awk '/^mattusifer/{print $2;}' $HOME/.imapinfo"
AuthMechs PLAIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile ~/gmail-cert.pem

IMAPStore mattusifer-remote
Account mattusifer

MaildirStore mattusifer-local
Path ~/mail/mattusifer/
Inbox ~/mail/mattusifer/INBOX

Channel mattusifer
Master :mattusifer-remote:
Slave :mattusifer-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
